videos.description: Retin Obasohan goes in for the layup, but Dayton's Steve McElvene blocks him emphatically.
videos.headline: McElvene blocks Obasohan with authority

videos.description: Dayton's Scoochie Smith dives for the steal and pitches it ahead to teammate Kyle Davis for the easy layup
videos.headline: Scoochie Smith knocks it away and dives for the steal

videos.description: Dayton's Darrell Davis pitches the ball ahead to Charles Cooke, who finishes hard at the rim with a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Cooke throws down big two-handed jam

videos.description: Dayton's John Crosby with the nice bounce pass to teammate Bobby Wehrli who draws the foul on a layup
videos.headline: John Crosby finds Bobby Wehrli in the lane for a layup
